Tiny Todo changelog

Version 0.4 - 19.02.2014
 - Fixed common Sailfish UI pitfalls
 - New looks for todo list, note that glass ball logic has been inverted
 - Remove individual items from the list

 
Version 0.3 - 25.01.2014
 - Show four first undone items on the cover
 - Translation support
 - Finnish translation
 
 
Version 0.2
 - Fixed losing sync of item statuses between database and list view with long lists

 
Version 0.1
 - Initial release
